"# antd Components (6.4.4)

| Component | Name (zh) | Description | Since |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Affix | 固钉 | Stick an element to the viewport. |  |
| Alert | 警告提示 | Display warning messages that require attention. |  |
| Anchor | 锚点 | Hyperlinks to scroll on one page. |  |
| App | 包裹组件 | Application wrapper for some global usages. |  |
| AutoComplete | 自动完成 | Autocomplete function of input field. |  |
| Avatar | 头像 | Used to represent users or things, supporting the display of images, icons, or characters. |  |
| Badge | 徽标数 | Small numerical value or status descriptor for UI elements. |  |
| BorderBeam | 边框流光 | Decorative component that renders a moving beam along a container border. |  |
| Breadcrumb | 面包屑 | Display the current location within a hierarchy. And allow going back to states higher up in the hierarchy. |  |
| Button | 按钮 | To trigger an operation. |  |
| Calendar | 日历 | A container that displays data in calendar form. |  |
| Card | 卡片 | A container for displaying information. |  |
| Carousel | 走马灯 | A set of carousel areas. |  |
| Cascader | 级联选择 | Cascade selection box. |  |
| Checkbox | 多选框 | Collect user's choices. |  |
| Collapse | 折叠面板 | A content area which can be collapsed and expanded. |  |
| ColorPicker | 颜色选择器 | Used for color selection. |  |
| ConfigProvider | 全局化配置 | Provide a uniform configuration support for components. |  |
| DatePicker | 日期选择框 | To select or input a date. |  |
| Descriptions | 描述列表 | Display multiple read-only fields in a group. |  |
| Divider | 分割线 | A divider line separates different content. |  |
| Drawer | 抽屉 | A panel that slides out from the edge of the screen. |  |
| Dropdown | 下拉菜单 | A dropdown list. |  |
| Empty | 空状态 | Empty state placeholder. |  |
| Flex | 弹性布局 | A flex layout container for alignment. |  |
| FloatButton | 悬浮按钮 | A button that floats at the top of the page. |  |
| Form | 表单 | High-performance form component with data domain management. Includes data entry, validation, and corresponding styles. |  |
| Grid | 栅格 | 24 Grids System. |  |
| Icon | 图标 | Semantic vector graphics. |  |
| Image | 图片 | Preview-able image. |  |
| Input | 输入框 | Through mouse or keyboard input content, it is the most basic form field wrapper. |  |
| InputNumber | 数字输入框 | Enter a number within certain range with the mouse or keyboard. |  |
| Layout | 布局 | Handling the overall layout of a page. |  |
| List | 列表 | Basic list display, which can carry text, lists, pictures, paragraphs. |  |
| Masonry | 瀑布流 |  |  |
| Mentions | 提及 | Used to mention someone or something in an input. |  |
| Menu | 导航菜单 | A versatile menu for navigation. |  |
| Message | 全局提示 | Display global messages as feedback in response to user operations. |  |
| Modal | 对话框 | Display a modal dialog box, providing a title, content area, and action buttons. |  |
| Notification | 通知提醒框 | Prompt notification message globally. |  |
| Pagination | 分页 | A long list can be divided into several pages, and only one page will be loaded at a time. |  |
| Popconfirm | 气泡确认框 | Pop up a bubble confirmation box for an action. |  |
| Popover | 气泡卡片 | The floating card pops up when clicking/mouse hovering over an element. |  |
| Progress | 进度条 | Display the current progress of the operation. |  |
| QRCode | 二维码 | Components that can convert text into QR codes, and support custom color and logo. |  |
| Radio | 单选框 | Used to select a single state from multiple options. |  |
| Rate | 评分 | Used for rating operation on something. |  |
| Result | 结果 | Used to feedback the processing results of a series of operations. |  |
